<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10064958>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Habitus and morphological details of Anaclasiger zhudaiae, male. A. Dorsal habitus. B. Head and pronotum. C. Antenna, ventral. D. Metaventrite, showing posteromedial projection and setae. E. Mesotibia. F. Tergite 5 (VIII). G. Sternite 6 (VIII). H. Sternite 7 (IX). I, J. Aedeagus, ventral (I), and lateral (J). Scale bars: 0.5 mm in A; 0.3 mm in B–E; 0.1 mm in F–H; 0.2 mm in I, J." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10064958/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10064960>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. A, B. Ex-situ photographs of Anaclasiger zhudaiae beetles with their host, Nylanderia flaviabdominis ants." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10064960/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10064962>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. A. Distribution of Anaclasiger; circle—A. sinuaticollis, rectangle—A. zhudaiae, dotted outline indicates new record. B–D. Nylanderia flaviabdominis, host of A. zhudaiae; habitus, lateral (B), dorsal (C), and full face (D). Scale bars: 0.5 mm in B, C; 0.3 mm in D." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10064962/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

